Package ec.distributedME

Class Behaviours

java.lang.Object
ec.distributedME.Behaviours
All Implemented Interfaces:
Setup, Serializable, Cloneable
public class Behaviours extends Object implements Setup, Cloneable
Behaviours.java Instance of a single behaviour of the solution Holds the intervals and name for the behaviour Created: 25 January, 2022
Version:
1.0 Parameter example: map.behaviour.0.name = "behaviour1" map.behaviour.0.interval.0.ubound = 5 map.behaviour.0.interval.1.ubound = 10 map behaviour.1.name = "behaviour2" map.behaviour.1.interval.0.ubound = 12.5 map.behaviour.1.interval.1.ubound = 15.75 map.behaviour.1.interval.2.ubound = 25 map.behaviour.1.interval.3.ubound = 27.1 map.behaviour.1.interval.4.ubound = max max signifies max value for doubles
